dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddf25496ad2a9906ac03b7da595c5df7f545b4ab","tid":2210983,"uid":55493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0c3f8b65229637f523cf87a58650df64f51427b4","tid":2210983,"uid":60434,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我16維人睇到個post笑到收唔到聲"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想知16維人洗唔洗食飯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T02:08:06.000Z","msg":"16維仲有冇&ldquo;死&rdquo;呢樣野？<br />\n定其中一個世界死左但係其他世界未死，<br />\n算唔算死左？"},{"pid":"a9994ef8055141fe67921f1004c29145d5bff6d6","tid":2210983,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T02:13:06.000Z","msg":"強帖留名！ ！ ！"},{"pid":"73a3ed25b01e5a7196f01332cd1ae0993c0ccca1","tid":2210983,"uid":120123,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T02:19:25.000Z","msg":"但我反而咁睇，時間同三維空間本身係有interaction，唔係一個獨立的存在來。<br />\n即係你三維空間發生的事，例如重力/高速飛行，係會影嚮到時間。我認為係可以當係第四維 (當然，其實呢樣野都係前人定出來)。<br />\n<br />\n以前有人諗過一個theory出來，咁當然個theory係好有問題，但係幾有趣。<br />\n即係佢問，點解我地存在的空間。粒粒電子個樣都係一樣?<br />\n佢個答案係，因為每一粒電子都係同一粒電子。<br />\n佢就係當時間係第四維咁睇，如果我地畫個圖出來，空間係X axis，而時間係Y axis。<br />\n如果電子係一種可以嚮四維移動的粒子。我地嚮某個時間去量度佢，就只係嚮Y axis特定一條橫線上去睇。即係好似下圖咁<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gC7Faz8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgC7Faz8.jpg&h=ef250ebe&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n咁一粒電子就可以嚮同一個時間，嚮唔同地點出現。粒電子嚮Y axis行的方向就決定左佢係matter定antimatter。<br />\n<br />\n咁當然，成個theory最大問題係positrons係明顯少過electrons好多。呢樣野係解釋唔到，但其實如果當時間係第四維，其實都可以有d有趣的theory走到出來<br />\n<br />\nReference: Single electron universe"},{"pid":"a6beba611f510c5bdbacb1ae0a43e412cca19535","tid":2210983,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T02:20:19.000Z","msg":"咁點先係四維或上？<br />\n零維實質係咩？點解發現唔倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a0bb5eb0875e9496c1edd59b49491a4bcf43fc","tid":2210983,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T02:21:14.000Z","msg":"神秘台好多人都會扭曲各學科嘅概念，所以掌握個概念嘅定義對獨立思考尤其重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d6769092e3ff1e2035995e2f95defba49c707f","tid":2210983,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0c263f562ad3409d368a452e3a7b9b8c242b2cb","tid":2210983,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:47:07.000Z","msg":"果個project嘅方向其實係嘗試將一早否定咗嘅GOFAI喺現代用更高計算力嘅CPU同display去谷多次，睇下加埋新display嘅學習功能可唔可以養到隻有小朋友級數/動物級數嘅AI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後係預期之內嘅失敗，做到街到賣嘅果啲智能產品嘅功能，但係同智能真係完全冇關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦即係話，街到賣嘅嘅智能乜乜全部都係假野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T02:22:54.000Z","msg":"如果你對AI既標準係去到要同人一樣先叫AI,咁世上完全無AI啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5a69f35880bdadd56e0bc67c11ab0aac54c47b","tid":2210983,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c3f8b65229637f523cf87a58650df64f51427b4","tid":2210983,"uid":60434,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我16維人睇到個post笑到收唔到聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T02:23:23.000Z","msg":"邊個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89defa2f7d04c723c2531a2a1e42af7ce0d2f8ec","tid":2210983,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T02:47:31.000Z","msg":"睇思方導航話「1+1=2」係重言句，一路都唔明點解<br />\n可唔可以講解下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6da5eb57c4